window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>From the vast desert and the unknown dimensions in between, it's EVENING SANDS, with your host, Jon French!</i></p> <p>Luther Stenson arrives for his first night as an intern at the popular late-night paranormal radio program, <i>Evening Sands</i>. But when the show receives a mysterious call from a woman who only goes by the name Magnolia, Luther realizes he may be getting more than he bargained for.</p>"; 
